Let me get this straight, this is one of the last non Disney acquired Fox movies the studio isn't embarrassed to release in theaters? While movies like Triple Threat, The Dirt, Buster Scruggs (a Cohen bros movie!!!) are exiled to Netflix streaming, huh! Nanjani and Bautista need to hire back whatever agents they fired right after they made The Big Sick and Blade Runner 2049, today!
